  <brief_title>The Effect of Volatile Anesthetics Sevoflurane and Desflurane on Liver, Renal and Cardiovascular Systems During Liver Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Volatile Anesthetics Sevoflurane and Desflurane on Liver, Renal and Cardiovascular Systems During Liver Surgery</official_title>
